's nothing."],[6712,6812,"Move!"],[7233,7345,"Fuck!"],[7345,7445,"Don't just stand there."],[7445,7516,"Take them out!"]],"20":[[50,137,"What?"],[137,254,"On my turf?"],[329,420,"And some asshole"],[420,608,"actually laid a hand on my fiancée?"],[687,766,"Baby!"],[787,916,"It wasn't just me."],[916,1108,"My mom got hit, too."],[1108,1241,"She was trying to protect me."],[1241,1387,"Okay, who are they?"],[1387,1458,"Alright I want to know"],[1458,1570,"who is backing them."],[1570,1662,"Nobody!"],[1662,1800,"Just some broke-ass doctor"],[1800,1966,"who can't even afford first class."],[2075,2245,"A doctor?"],[2245,2391,"Wow."],[2391,2425,"Alright."],[2425,2579,"It appears the Wolf family has been"],[2579,2700,"quiet for far too long."],[2700,2825,"Even nobodies think they can"],[2825,2933,"piss on our name."],[2970,3033,"Okay."],[3091,3162,"I'm going to head down"],[3162,3266,"to the airport myself."],[3341,3495,"They are going to learn real fast"],[3495,3595,"who they messed with."],[3687,3758,"Stay safe."],[3758,3862,"Of course, Baby."],[3912,4062,"Those worthless scum,"],[4129,4245,"today"],[4245,4516,"they'll learn exactly what it costs"],[4516,4729,"when you cross the Wolf family."],[4958,5162,"Mom, how's it feel now?"],[5162,5304,"I'm fine."],[5304,5491,"Let's finish those bastards off."],[5670,5908,"John, what the hell happened?"],[5908,6070,"I couldn't stop him."],[6100,6216,"The bitch with him"],[6216,6391,"was a goddamn monster."],[6833,6979,"Wait, how much longer?"],[7020,7158,"About six minutes."],[7333,7387,"We're good."],[7387,7508,"That's plenty of time."],[7700,7787,"I think we're actually going to pull this"],[7787,7866,"off, huh?"],[8545,8625,"Boss?"],[8625,8812,"Ada, why aren't you at the clinic yet?"],[8812,8895,"We're en route."],[8937,9091,"Ran into some trouble at the airport."],[9091,9166,"A mother daughter pair"],[9166,9245,"jumped Dr. Gray."],[9245,9320,"What?"],[9320,9437,"Who the hell are they?"],[9437,9662,"Who dare touch a Wolf family do