You've all got a death wish."],[2762,2933,"You lay hands on a Wolf family?"],[3004,3204,"Please."],[3204,3458,"A bitch like you actually works"],[3458,3600,"for the Wolf family?"],[3820,3962,"Let a truck come flatten me,"],[3962,4033,"right now."],[4179,4233,"See, John?"],[4233,4270,"I told you"],[4270,4454,"these two were totally faking it."],[4454,4595,"I am with the Wolf family."],[4645,4787,"Still going with that line?"],[5000,5116,"Come on over, sis."],[5170,5345,"Come teach this bitch"],[5345,5458,"who laid hands on you"],[5458,5637,"a lesson she'll never forget."],[5637,5787,"What's wrong?"],[5787,5995,"Not so cocky now, huh?"],[6054,6150,"Didn't I say I was going to"],[6150,6287,"make you pay?"],[6416,6587,"You fucking bitch."]],"23":[[79,245,"Fucking bitch!"],[875,1095,"Cat got your tongue, huh?"],[1095,1300,"I thought you were so tough."],[1300,1395,"Weren't you"],[1395,1604,"just saying you were going to kill me?"],[1604,1733,"What happened?"],[1733,1850,"Come on, get up."],[1850,1983,"Let's keep the act going."],[2254,2362,"Now you see who's"],[2362,2662,"really going to die."],[3245,3350,"Do you have any idea"],[3350,3437,"what happens with people"],[3437,3595,"who put hands on the Wolf family?"],[3595,3725,"You and that clown in the car are"],[3725,3908,"perfect for each other."],[3908,4133,"Both filthy liars."],[4133,4433,"Still lying, even this close to death."],[4458,4591,"Do you know what happens to people"],[4591,4833,"who pretend to be with the Wolf family?"],[4833,5104,"Why won't you believe me?"],[5175,5362,"You want to know why?"],[5362,5550,"I'll tell you why."],[5550,5850,"My fiancé is Eric Wolf."],[5954,6166,"The heir to the Wolf family."],[6166,6358,"What did you just say?"],[6358,6500,"What's wrong sweetheart?"],[6500,6583,"Finally scared?"],[6583,6712,"Listen to me."],[6712,6950,"I really am of the Wolf family."],[6950,7033,"If you don't believe me,"],[7033,7237,"just call Mr. Wolf himself and ask."],[7237,7337,"He'll tell you I'm telling the truth."],[7337,7383,"And now,"],[7383,7491,"why the hell would"],[7491,7620,"I believe anything you say?"],[7725,7904,"Jess, it's Erik."],[8104,8175,"Hi, Baby."],[8195,8350,"Hey, gorgeous, where you at?"],[8358,8470,"I'm on my way to come get you."],[8470,8587,"Mr. Wolf, Mr. Wolf, It's Ada!"],[8625,8683,"Honey, what..."],[8733,8829,"What was that?"],[8829,9070,"I swear, I just heard my dad's driver, Ada."],[9087,9220,"Why is she with you?"],[9300,9395,"What?"],[9475,9716,"Jess, is she really with the Wolf family?"]],"24":[[0,62,"Erik."],[112,187,"Who is Ada?"],[187,275,"Just a driver."],[275,387,"I mean, the Wolf family's got"],[387,512,"employees just crawling"],[512,625,"out of the woodwork."],[625,737,"Why? Babe, What’s up?"],[737,900,"Oh, so she's just an employee"],[900,1016,"of the Wolf family?"],[1029,1262,"Eric, that worthless bitch at the airport"],[1262,1387,"who put hands on me the other day,"],[1412,1500,"that was her."],[1500,1712,"What! That piece of shit actually hit you?"],[1712,1812,"Was does Ada think she can just throw"],[1812,1925,"her weight around now"],[1925,2075,"because she's my dad's driver?"],[2075,2312,"No, and she's laying hands on my fiancé."],[2312,2450,"Put me on speakerphone!"],[2600,2750,"Thank god."],[2750,2950,"Once Ada proves who she is,"],[2950,3062,"this nightmare is over."],[3125,3275,"Mr. Wolf, it's Ada."],[3275,3362,"I'm here on your father’s"],[3362,3450,"direct orders."],[3450,3562,"I'm here with Doctor Gray."],[3600,3700,"There was"],[3712,3837,"a misunderstanding in the airport"],[3837,3887,"with your fiancé."],[3900,3987,"That's all. I just -"],[3987,4087,"I don't care."],[4087,4250,"I don't care what your excuse is."],[4250,4375,"You laid hands on Jess."],[4400,4512,"So you're dead."],[4512,4575,"Period."],[4587,4662,"Mr. Wolf!"],[4662,4775,"Please listen to me."],[4825,4912,"It's your grandfather, he-"],[4912,5000,"Step on it."],[5000,5050,"Mr. Wolf!"]],"25":[[16,129,"Mr. Wolf!"],[304,516,"You had me going there for a second."],[554,663,"I actually thought you might be some"],[663,884,"big shit for the Wolf family."],[958,1204,"But you are just the help."],[1312,1412,"A lowly servant"],[1412,1629,"who dares strike her master."],[1712,1870,"You have some goddamn nerve."],[1929,2079,"Look, I'm sorry."],[2083,2185,"Ok, I had no idea you were"],[2185,2285,"Mr. Wolf's fiancé."],[2287,2383,"I apologize."],[2383,2515,"Do whatever you want with me later"],[2515,2610,"but please, I beg you."],[2612,2741,"Let Doctor Gray go."],[2766,2875,"You want me to let him go?"],[2962,3066,"Not a chance."],[3075,3150,"I told you,"],[3150,3266,"I'm going to make both of you guys"],[3266,3362,"pay for this."],[3404,3454,"John,"],[3454,3612,"drag the lying piece of shit out of the car."],[3754,3925,"No, no! Stop! Don't do this."],[3975,4120,"Listen, I'm going to tell the truth."],[4179,4250,"Okay."],[4258,4370,"Mr. Wolf's grandfather"],[4370,4487,"is in critical condition."],[4495,4675,"He needs a kidney transplant right now."],[4675,4795,"That's why Doctor Gray's here."],[4804,4929,"He's rushing to save your future"],[4929,5104,"grandfather-in-law's life."],[5129,5275,"Fucking bitch."],[5316,5533,"Still cursing Eric's grandpa, huh?"],[5554,5691,"I'll bash your damn head in."],[5750,5804,"Wait."]],"26":[[416,462,"What's up?"],[462,550,"Why did you stop me?"],[650,741,"That driver,"],[804,912,"what she was saying was exactly"],[912,1079,"what the guy in the car was saying."],[1100,1175,"Relax."],[1262,1362,"Clearly, the two of them"],[1362,1500,"are in on it together."],[1570,1675,"Total scam."],[1675,1837,"Yeah, didn't you call Erik on the plane"],[1837,1920,"and ask about his grandpa?"],[1920,2087,"Didn't he say that Derek was fine?"],[2087,2204,"Yeah, but that woman,"],[2204,2287,"she"],[2287,2466,"really is one of the Wolf family's people."],[2500,2629,"Then call Erik again."],[2629,2758,"Confirm it straight from him."],[3070,3179,"Hey, baby."],[3179,3262,"One more thing."],[3262,3395,"Your grandpa, Derek Wolf."],[3395,3550,"He really is okay, right?"],[3550,3629,"Of course. I mean,"],[3629,3712,"if there was something wrong"],[3712,3758,"with my grandpa,"],[3758,3862,"don't you think I'd know?"],[3879,4033,"Yeah, but that bitch, Ada, she,"],[4033,4120,"she swears that"],[4170,4320,"he's sick and in the hospital."],[4366,4475,"Alright, alright. Fine. I'll,"],[4475,4562,"I'll just call my dad,"],[4562,4675,"get it straight from him."],[4675,4750,"I'm almost there. Okay."],[4750,4895,"So we'll just handle this in person."],[5529,5708,"Have you found Ada and Doctor Gray yet?"],[5708,5808,"Yeah, boss."],[5808,5891,"Last ping showed"],[5891,6066,"that they stopped on highway 112"],[6095,6200,"near Coal Park."],[6275,6366,"God damn it!"],[6366,6541,"Something really has happened, hasn't it?"],[6570,6687,"Relax, boss."],[6687,6791,"Ada just has to say that"],[6791,6950,"she's with the Wolf family."],[6950,7054,"No one's crazy enough"],[7054,7162,"to mess with her."],[7162,7266,"And guess you're right."]],"27":[[266,350,"Erik."],[350,537,"Why the hell is he calling me?"],[604,670,"What do you want?"],[708,891,"Hey, dad, where are you right now?"],[900,987,"At the office, why?"],[1012,1108,"Oh, good."],[1108,1254,"I'm actually on the way to the airport"],[1254,1350,"to pick up Jess."],[1350,1500,"Her and her mom flew in to visit."],[1500,1620,"Thought maybe you and mom"],[1620,1725,"would come out to meet them."],[1770,1862,"They'd be thrilled."],[1862,2108,"I don't have time for that right now."],[2129,2212,"Okay, I mean,"],[2212,2366,"what about tomorrow or"],[2366,2470,"the day after that?"],[2508,2633,"We'll see."],[2683,2737,"Wait."],[2762,2854,"Did you say you're on your way"],[2854,2962,"to the airport right now?"],[2966,3070,"Yeah. Why?"],[3170,3325,"Great, change your route."],[3325,3612,"Go to highway 112 near Coal’s Park."],[3612,3745,"See if Ada’s there."],[3758,3854,"Whether she is or not,"],[3854,4029,"you call me the second you know."],[4029,4091,"Got it?"],[4091,4225,"Dad, what's going on?"],[4225,4383,"You seem kind of pissed right now."],[4383,4575,"Did Ada screw something up again?"],[4575,4666,"Dad, I told you,"],[4666,4820,"she's nothing but trouble."],[4837,4941,"Just do what I tell you"],[4941,5087,"and stop running your mouth."],[5087,5170,"Alright, alright."],[5241,5337,"Just wait for my call then."],[5495,5579,"Judging by that tone,"],[5579,5720,"that useless bitch, Ada,"],[5720,5829,"really pissed him off."]],"28":[[16,145,"This is perfect."],[183,400,"Ada, first you lay hands on my fiancée,"],[450,654,"then you manage to tick my dad off too?"],[704,800,"There’s going to be no one left"],[800,887,"to save your ass."],[925,1058,"Let's see how I make you pay,"],[1116,1225,"with your life."],[1283,1345,"One more thing."],[1358,1520,"Your grandpa, Derek Wolf."],[1562,1708,"He really is okay, right?"],[1754,1862,"If there was something wrong"],[1862,1941,"with my grandpa,"],[1941,2041,"no way my dad"],[2041,2241,"would still be sitting in the office."],[2270,2420,"Ada Cane, you dumb bitch,"],[2420,2550,"cursing my grandpa"],[2550,2670,"just to scam Jessica."],[2737,2920,"You really wanna die that badly?"],[3191,3345,"I swear I'm not lying."],[3358,3437,"Mr. Wolf’s grandfather"],[3437,3583,"doesn't have too much time."],[3583,3650,"Relax."],[3675,3816,"Erik will be here any second."],[3841,3937,"If you're telling the truth,"],[3937,4079,"then I'll let you walk."],[4079,4183,"Simple as that."],[5183,5279,"Baby!"]],"29":[[0,104,"Baby!"],[283,416,"You miss me that much?"],[508,658,"And you must be Miss Hansen."],[845,1000,"Jess, I see where you get it from."],[1004,1154,"Absolutely stunning."],[1154,1233,"I want to thank you both"],[1233,1316,"for making the trip."],[1316,1525,"Oh, no, really, it's nothing."],[1658,1958,"Welcome to Miami."],[2166,2250,"Mr. Wolf."],[2500,2591,"Oh."],[2633,2729,"Well, look who it is."],[2816,2883,"Jeez. Ada."],[2883,3004,"Ada, what happened to you?"],[3004,3100,"You look like she got run over"],[3100,3254,"by a garbage truck."],[3354,3437,"The doctor."],[3437,3575,"Please, we have to hurry."],[3583,3733,"I'm sorry. What? The doctor?"],[3795,3900,"Oh, you want me to rush this idiot"],[3900,3991,"to the clinic so he can"],[3991,4108,"cut my grandfather open?"],[4108,4141,"Yes."],[4170,4250,"Please, we have-"]],"30":[[29,150,"You are one miserable"],[170,312,"excuse of a human being."],[312,383,"You know that?"],[400,508,"Because I talked to my dad."],[583,712,"And my grandfather's just fine."],[750,891,"So this whore was lying."],[975,1029,"Told you."],[1029,1204,"Her and this clown in the car,"],[1204,1295,"lying through their teeth."],[1341,1441,"Total scam."],[1445,1533,"Disgusting."],[1550,1641,"An employee"],[1654,1770,"daring to curse her own"],[1770,1875,"boss's family."],[1900,1983,"Mr. Wolf?"],[2054,2200,"Did your father really say that?"],[2208,2379,"Let me call you in on something."],[2412,2641,"He's pissed at you big time."],[2700,2783,"There's no way, no."],[2862,2958,"Must be because I failed."],[3000,3170,"I failed to protect Doctor Gray."],[3170,3258,"Enough."],[3258,3425,"John, grab the lying piece of shit"],[3425,3512,"out of the car."],[4020,4083,"Run!"],[4445,4587,"Well, don't just stand there."],[4587,4650,"Grab him!"]],"31":[[4,62,"Run!"],[166,279,"Run, Dr. Gray, don't stop."],[279,379,"Just run."],[1408,1487,"Run, run!"],[1487,1604,"Where are you gonna run?"],[1604,1729,"Every square inch of Miami"],[1729,1904,"is covered under my family's boot."],[1954,2050,"Mr. Wolf."],[2050,2100,"Please."],[2133,2216,"Beat me all you want."],[2245,2395,"But I beg you, let Doctor Gray go."],[2512,2604,"You want me to stop?"],[2604,2762,"You're kidding, right?"],[2762,2983,"I can beat whoever the hell I want."],[2983,3175,"This worthless slut."],[3175,3287,"She's with the Wolf family,"],[3287,3475,"yet she sides with an outsider."],[3525,3766,"If I were me, I'd have killed her already."],[3825,4033,"Baby, look at my face, it's all swollen."],[4033,4154,"It's all her fault."],[4479,4587,"You see that kidney?"],[4587,4712,"Doctor Gray’s carrying."],[4754,4912,"It’s the only match for your grandfather,"],[4925,4983,"Derek Wolf."],[5029,5154,"Let him go."],[5154,5283,"Or your family will lose"],[5283,5450,"way more than face."],[5700,5870,"Call your father."],[5908,6041,"Fix this."],[6125,6279,"I'm sorry, I'm sorry."],[6279,6475,"Are you trying to give me orders now?"],[6475,6666,"Who the hell do you think you are?"],[6666,6900,"You're just a mutt we let live on scraps."],[8000,8033,"Dad?"]],"32":[[16,137,"You find Ada yet?"],[179,241,"Yeah, yeah."],[241,379,"No, she's right here with me."],[379,433,"Great."],[433,587,"Get her to the clinic ASAP."],[587,670,"I'll meet you there."],[670,758,"Got it."],[887,954,"Clinic?"],[1079,1295,"Oh, I get it, I get it."],[1295,1454,"It's a day my dad goes and visits"],[1454,1600,"my grandpa like he does every month."],[1625,1745,"Oh my God, baby."],[1745,1854,"Are you telling me we might"],[1854,2058,"actually meet the Derek Wolf?"],[2058,2237,"The arms legend himself?"],[2245,2391,"That's exactly what I'm saying."],[2391,2508,"This is incredible."],[2508,2616,"Meeting Derek Wolf."],[2616,2716,"What an honor."],[2716,2791,"Not just anyone"],[2791,2937,"gets to meet my grandfather."],[2962,3100,"No, no, no, the fact that my dad's"],[3100,3225,"even willing to bring you all around"],[3225,3437,"shows how serious he is about us."],[3483,3575,"Now, I know y'all would never,"],[3575,3758,"but just please don't mess this up, okay?"],[3758,3870,"Oh, don't worry, baby."],[3870,3945,"I'll make sure to show him my"],[3945,4058,"absolute best side."],[4083,4158,"Exactly."],[4158,4379,"And if Erik's father is introducing us,"],[4379,4504,"then that just proves"],[4541,4683,"those two pieces of trash"],[4683,4841,"were lying the whole time."],[4858,4970,"Don't worry about that. No."],[4970,5125,"My dad is way harsher than I am."],[5166,5233,"He’ll handle it."],[5345,5583,"He passed out after a couple of hits."],[5583,5704,"Soft as butter."],[5737,5875,"Thank you so much, John."],[5887,5979,"Take those two idiots"],[5979,6095,"and throw them in the back of the trunk."],[6095,6204,"My dad will handle them."],[6300,6425,"And this?"],[6454,6516,"I don't know, man."],[6516,6691,"I mean, just bring it just in case, alright."],[6691,6870,"My dad will take a look at it."],[6870,7029,"If it's useless, he'll trash it."],[7075,7208,"Alright, load them up."]],"33":[[350,500,"Hey, cut it out."],[500,608,"Save it for tonight, baby."],[654,820,"But, seriously, thanks for putting those"],[820,987,"nobodies in their place for me today."],[987,1162,"Well, listen, that's just two dirtbags"],[1162,1333,"trying to bring my family name down."],[1333,1520,"Then laying a hand on my woman?"],[1566,1783,"Yeah, it's about a suicidal as it gets."],[1783,1933,"You're too good to me."],[1933,2095,"I still can't believe it."],[2095,2200,"Soon I'm officially going to be"],[2200,2308,"a part of the Wolf family."],[2308,2529,"I feel like I'm living in a dream."],[2529,2608,"Soon?"],[2641,2750,"Who says soon?"],[2750,2820,"My dad letting you"],[2820,2958,"meet my grandfather?"],[2958,3112,"That means you're already family."],[3112,3295,"That's just him endorsing you."],[4020,4091,"Boss."],[4091,4166,"Here they come."],[4250,4400,"25 minutes left."],[4400,4520,"Plenty of time."],[4520,4600,"Looks like my father's"],[4600,4662,"going to make it."],[4804,4895,"Erik's never pulled off"],[4895,5033,"anything right in his life."],[5075,5158,"Looks like there's a first"],[5158,5275,"time for everything."]],"34":[[8,95,"Looks like there's a first"],[95,262,"time for everything."],[262,408,"Oh, look."],[408,566,"That's my dad right there."],[566,637,"I can't believe he actually"],[637,679,"came out here"],[679,791,"to meet us personally."],[858,1025,"It's all thanks to you, sweetheart."],[1025,1129,"That's him?"],[1129,1350,"That's the CEO of Wolf Industries?"],[1350,1462,"God