ing now."]],"40":[[45,150,"Hey, relax, baby."],[150,283,"We got nothing to worry about."],[283,391,"That damn delivery boy,"],[391,462,"he's still breathing."],[462,608,"The kidney's just fine."],[608,687,"We're all right."],[687,762,"But, what if-"],[762,829,"Oh come on, I'm"],[845,950,"my dad's only son."],[950,1058,"I am the sole heir"],[1058,1216,"to the entire Wolf Industries"],[1216,1279,"empire."],[1295,1408,"No matter how pissed he is"],[1408,1450,"right now,"],[1450,1587,"once my grandpa wakes up,"],[1587,1729,"I get to plead with him, I'm..."],[1845,1987,"I'm sure he'll agree to let you marry me."],[2212,2266,"Alright."],[2295,2420,"Alright, I've got our engagement party"],[2420,2487,"all lined up."],[2529,2679,"Huh, why don't we just go celebrate?"]],"41":[[170,237,"Dr. Gray,"],[325,416,"my father, how is he?"],[566,691,"The surgery was a success."],[1270,1341,"Wait, wait, wait."],[1420,1566,"Grandpa's surgery was a success?"],[1895,2008,"I mean, didn't I say so?"],[2141,2254,"Alright."],[2495,2591,"Alright."],[2600,2695,"Alright."],[2779,2941,"Here's to my grandpa's recovery."],[2995,3091,"It's me and Jess"],[3091,3212,"finally getting engaged."],[3266,3300,"Tonight,"],[3391,3425,"oh,"],[3450,3645,"tonight we drink until we drop."],[3754,3850,"Hell, yeah."],[4425,4516,"Thank you, Dr. Gray."],[4516,4662,"You have saved my family,"],[4766,4829,"Thank you."],[4829,4891,"Dr. Gray,"],[4891,5037,"the patient's going into acute rejection."]],"42":[[58,104,"Dr. Gray,"],[104,229,"what's happening with my father?"],[229,333,"Why is he like this?"],[333,483,"The delays during transport"],[483,612,"cost us precious time."],[720,816,"By the time we operated,"],[816,895,"your father's body was"],[895,995,"already in bad condition."],[1062,1183,"That's why he's crashing now."],[1183,1266,"Then what do we do?"],[1266,1425,"Tell me there's still a way."],[1541,1600,"Right now,"],[1600,1791,"the only option is to do a biopsy."],[1858,1991,"So then we can figure out exactl