. Gray's fault."],[5329,5416,"If he hadn't stalled,"],[5416,5491,"your grandpa wouldn't"],[5491,5700,"even be in this mess."],[5916,6091,"You shut your fucking mouth!"],[6158,6320,"You smear Dr. Gray one more time,"],[6320,6433,"and I swear to God,"],[6433,6583,"I will have you chopped up and"],[6583,6675,"fed to my dogs."]],"60":[[12,141,"Jess, Jess!"],[141,229,"Mr. Wolf,"],[229,404,"what the hell is wrong with you?"],[404,550,"This is your son's fiancée,"],[550,658,"we're family now."],[658,737,"She's right, Dad."],[737,775,"Okay?"],[775,983,"So please, just calm down."],[1058,1120,"Calm down?"],[1204,1320,"You want me to calm down,"],[1320,1404,"when your grandfather"],[1404,1545,"is in there fighting for his life,"],[1545,1629,"and all you care about"],[1629,1800,"is your stupid fiancée?"],[1800,1879,"Yeah, yeah!"],[1879,2008,"Calm down, okay dad?"],[2008,2191,"I mean, Grandpa's just in surgery,"],[2191,2287,"Alright? He's not going to die."],[2300,2404,"That's what this doctor's here for"],[2404,2433,"right?"],[2433,2525,"So why you gonna lose your head?"],[2575,2804,"You cold hearted bastard."],[3016,3200,"You two better start praying"],[3200,3337,"that my father walks out"],[3337,3545,"of this hospital alive."],[3616,3754,"Because if he doesn't,"],[3995,4258,"you two will see just how far"],[4258,4408,"my wrath can go."],[5004,5291,"Dr. Gray, my father,"],[5291,5425,"how is he?"],[5945,6058,"I'm sorry, Mr. Wolf."],[6208,6445,"I did everything I could,"],[6445,6612,"but your father..."],[6612,6695,"he's gone."]],"61":[[154,304,"What did you just say?"],[304,437,"My grandpa?"],[437,466,"Dead?"],[466,675,"No, that's total bullshit!"],[675,883,"My grandpa can't be dead."],[883,1066,"Erik, it's got to be this hack's fault."],[1066,1204,"He's incompetent."],[1204,1300,"He botched the surgery"],[1300,1412,"and killed your grandpa."],[1412,1537,"You worthless bastard."],[1537,1608,"How did you screw"],[1608,1804,"up so bad you killed him?"],[1804,1904,"Maybe that's the question"],[1904,2154,"you should be asking yourself, Erik."],[2154,2283,"And your precious fiancée."],[2283,2412,"It was you! Shut up."],[2412,2558,"It was all you."],[2850,3000,"The only one who needs to shut"],[3000,3245,"the hell up is you."],[3245,3320,"Mr. Wolf."],[3320,3462,"No, you can't listen to him."],[3462,3612,"I swear I didn't."],[3612,3679,"It was him."],[3679,3795,"It was - Fuck off."],[4195,4354,"Go ahead, Dr. Gray."],[4429,4608,"Tell me everything."],[4720,4895,"It was your son's fiancée,"],[5008,5112,"and her mother,"],[5112,5266,"that delayed us on the tarmac,"],[5266,5412,"Mr. Wolf."],[5458,5587,"Later,"],[5587,5800,"after we landed,"],[5800,5966,"they had people chasing us,"],[6004,6100,"blocking us,"],[6150,6237,"and stopping us"],[6237,6395,"from getting to the clinic on time."],[6395,6475,"They're the reason"],[6475,6629,"we lost precious hours."],[6920,6983,"Jess,"],[7095,7258,"is what he's saying true?"],[7287,7416,"No, no, baby, please."]],"62":[[33,158,"Is what he's saying true?"],[200,345,"No, no, baby, please."],[345,520,"You can't listen to him, he's lying, I-"],[520,725,"Oh, shut up!"],[725,912,"Look me in the eyes and tell me"],[912,1025,"if it's true or not."],[1029,1100,"Stop it, Erik."],[1100,1179,"Have you lost your mind?"],[1179,1362,"That's your fiancée you're choking."],[1462,1633,"Get off me, you old hag!"],[1729,1845,"Say it."],[1845,1954,"Say it,"],[1954,2300,"or I swear I'll kill you right here."],[2575,2662,"I was wrong."],[2662,2837,"Okay?"],[2837,3020,"I'm so sorry, Erik."],[3020,3283,"Just please, please don't hurt me."],[3283,3420,"You think I'm going to let you slide?"],[3504,3729,"I should kill you for what you've done."],[4433,4566,"Dr. Gray, please."],[4566,4645,"Please, I am begging you."],[4645,4870,"I was a fool, I am wrong, I'm so sorry."],[4870,5070,"Please just save my grandpa."],[5070,5125,"Please."],[5125,5233,"I will give you my kidney."],[5233,5366,"I will do anything, please!"],[5366,5566,"Please, just save him."],[5666,5833,"It's too late now, Erik."],[5833,6025,"Your grandfather's already gone."],[6104,6337,"His body shut down."],[6412,6583,"Besides, even if I had another kidney,"],[6695,6825,"there's nothing left to save."]],"63":[[12,312,"There's nothing left to save."],[662,904,"You worthless piece of shit."],[904,1016,"You think either one of these"],[1016,1183,"crazy bitches would've dared do"],[1183,1266,"anything against us"],[1266,1450,"without your backing?"],[1595,1837,"You're gonna meet your grandfather,"],[1837,2137,"and you're gonna beg for his forgiveness."],[2283,2462,"No, Dad, please, please stop!"],[2462,2520,"I'm sorry."],[2520,2650,"I'm sorry."],[2650,2812,"Dad!"],[2875,2987,"I'm sorry, I was wrong."],[2987,3050,"Okay?"],[3050,3233,"Please, just don't hit me anymore."],[3629,3704,"Dad?"],[3704,3916,"You think this is just about you?"],[3916,4075,"God damn it, Erik."],[4075,4308,"I'm the fool that made you this way."],[4308,4454,"I spoiled you."],[4454,4654,"I turned a blind eye."],[4654,4954,"And this is what you've done."],[5270,5441,"I did this."],[5441,5833,"I raised you to be a selfish monster."],[5904,5970,"No, Dad,"],[5970,6270,"we still have money, Dad!"],[6350,6445,"You idiot."],[6445,6570,"Don't you get it?"],[6570,6779,"Wolf Industries is finished."],[6779,6908,"We're staring bankruptcy"],[6908,7095,"in the face because of you."]],"64":[[41,91,"Oh, no, no,"],[91,208,"no, you've got to be kidding me."],[208,491,"No, we just did a $5 billion deal."],[491,741,"We cannot be going bankrupt."],[741,954,"You think this family's empire"],[954,1100,"was built on luck?"],[1100,1387,"Your grandfather's connections."],[1387,1612,"His leverage on governments"],[1612,1808,"and private armies worldwide."],[1808,2020,"That's how we flourished."],[2020,2170,"You think"],[2170,2283,"arms business"],[2283,2454,"is that goddamn simple?"],[2537,2662,"Now he's gone."],[2733,2979,"And all of our contracts are voided,"],[3033,3295,"because they were all tied to him."],[3295,3500,"Personally."],[3500,3587,"What are you saying?"],[3587,3958,"I'm saying the Wolf empire is finished."],[4062,4308,"We're dead broke, Erik."],[4400,4516,"No, no, no, no, no."],[4608,4650,"Baby,"],[4700,4745,"hey."],[4791,4950,"Are you okay?"],[5025,5116,"You."],[5245,5350,"You."],[5470,5658,"This is all your fault."]],"65":[[4,179,"This is all your fault."],[316,487,"You filthy bitch!"],[487,683,"I ought to kill you!"],[4354,4545,"A broken body will heal."],[4545,4704,"But a broken soul?"],[4704,4900,"That's another story."],[4975,5275,"Hey, if you could do it all over again,"],[5275,5525,"and still risk your life to save him,"],[5595,5787,"would you?"],[5912,6212,"Honestly,"],[6229,6529,"I don't know."],[7350,7516,"But I guess, yeah."],[7516,7687,"I probably would."],[7770,7970,"Because I'm a doctor."],[8075,8191,"Take care, Ada."]]}